OL,3,CMan jailed over violent disorder at
OL,4,Casylum seeker hotel
OL,6,FThe Farnham man was arrested at
OL,7,FGatwick Airport on return from his
OL,8,FDubai holiday on August 19 after he
OL,9,Fdid not appear at magistrates' court
OL,10,Ffollowing the incident.
OL,12,FHe was brought before Basingstoke
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court on Tuesday where he
OL,14,Fpleaded guilty to violent disorder and
OL,15,Fa bail act offence.
OL,17,FWinchester Crown Court on Wednesday
OL,18,Fheard how 85 families were living in
OL,19,Fthe hotel and there were people inside
OL,20,Fthe accommodation in "great fear" of
OL,21,Fwhat was going to happen to them.
