OL,3,CMan jailed over violent disorder at
OL,4,Casylum seeker hotel
OL,6,FAround #1,900 worth of damage was also
OL,7,Fcaused from the disorder after a small
OL,8,Fgroup of protesters got into the hotel
OL,9,Fcar park at around 6.40pm and more and
OL,10,Fmore joined them.
OL,12,FJudge Nigel Lickley KC described how
OL,13,FFisher threw the children's scooter
OL,14,F"with force" at the hotel and there
OL,15,Fwas a loud bang and cheering from the
OL,16,Fcrowd as a result.
OL,18,FThe bikes had been provided for the
OL,19,Fhotel residents to use, the court
OL,20,Fheard.
