OL,4,Casylum seeker hotel
OL,6,FProsecutor Tim Devlin said a large
OL,7,Fcrowd started shouting 'illegals out',
OL,8,F'we want our community back'.
OL,10,FHe added the police were "massively
OL,11,Foutnumbered" and the situation was
OL,12,F"rapidly getting out of hand".
OL,14,FIn mitigation the court heard the act
OL,15,Fwas "out of character" for the new dad
OL,16,Fwho felt remorse for what he had done.
