OL,4,Casylum seeker hotel
OL,6,FSentencing Fisher, Judge Lickley said
OL,7,Fthe occupants of the hotel were the
OL,8,F"real target" of Fisher's actions
OL,9,Fwhich were fuelled by hostility over
OL,10,Frace and religion.
OL,12,F"The sole purpose of activity, of
OL,13,Fwhich you were one, was to intimidate
OL,14,Fand frighten the occupants of the
OL,15,Fbuilding", he said.
OL,17,F"The mob you were part of was very
OL,18,Fintimidating."
