OL,4,Casylum seeker hotel
OL,6,FHe added that while Fisher had asked
OL,7,Ffor his court hearing to be adjourned
OL,8,Fbefore going on holiday he showed a
OL,9,F"cavalier attitude to the courts and
OL,10,Fserious offence you faced" by missing
OL,11,Fhis court date.
OL,13,FFisher was sentenced to 29 months'
OL,14,Fimprisonment for both offences.
OL,16,FHe will be released from prison after
OL,17,Fserving half of his sentence and will
OL,18,Fspend the rest on licence, the judge
OL,19,Fsaid.
