OL,6,FFisher has received the longest
OL,7,Fsentence within the Wessex region,
OL,8,Faccording to the Crown Prosecution
OL,9,FService.
OL,11,FCPS Wessex deputy chief crown
OL,12,Fprosecutor, Sophie Stevens, said:
OL,13,F"Fisher's part in the violent disorder
OL,14,Fseen in Aldershot has not only
OL,15,Fendangered vulnerable individuals but
OL,16,Fhas also disrupted the peace and
OL,17,Fsecurity of our communities.
